        Constructor of DbConnector implementation class for establishing a connection to a MySQL database.
        Parameters:
        host - The IP of the machine where the database is hosted.
        port - The port where the database is listening.
        dbName - The name of the database to connect to.
        username - The user name credential to access the database.
        password - The password credential to access the database.
